GET /api/nodes/{nodeId}/endpoints
  List all API endpoints exposed by a service
  Response: APIEndpoint[]

POST /api/nodes/{nodeId}/endpoints
  Create a new endpoint (usually via OpenAPI sync)
  Body: { method, path, operationId, ... }
  Response: APIEndpoint (201)

GET /api/endpoints/{id}
  Fetch endpoint with consumers and usage stats
  Response: APIEndpoint { consumers, callsPerDay, errorRate, ... }

PUT /api/endpoints/{id}
  Mark as deprecated, update SLA, etc.
  Body: { deprecated, sunsetDate, deprecationMessage, ... }
  Response: APIEndpoint

GET /api/endpoints/{id}/consumers
  List services that call this endpoint
  Response: ServiceConsumer[]
